title: Possible Expansion of The Project?
body:
Hello Everyone!!! As we all know prices on Etherium have been anything but User friendly. I am not sure if anyone is aware, but the Binace Smart Chain is currently
active and is having a massive transfer of users. I  just wrote a whole big thing out, so I will keep it this short. I know many projects have had their tokens moved over, many more are, and many more are discussing it. The fact is, no one knows when for sure Etherium transaction prices will get better, meanwhile, the price only seems to increase, while. So, this vote is not on transferring over. It is a vote on whether we should discuss the possibility of it. Thank you so much for your time and ear. 
Happy Inovating.
